<plot>Sandy goes to the prom with her boyfriend, Bill. Bill has just bought a new car and is anxious to show Sandy what it can do. The two of them go speeding around town in his car, only to wind up crashing into a tree, which kills them both. Moral: Speed--and not going to a place you told your parents you were going to--kills.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?569696</url></doc>
